title: 07/23: QB Week! Sleeper QBs, Two-QB Leagues, and More (Fantasy Football Podcast)
description:
Starting QB week off with our QB sleepers and a review of our recent 2QB draft. Also discussing Josh Gordon and all the relevant training camp news. Plus we put Alvin Kamara under the microscope and answer your emails at FantasyFootball@CBSi.com
